race.description: Rural City Of Murray Bridge Grade 5 Series F Pr1 D
race.comment: TIME TO FIRE (4) has a terrific record here with four wins and three placings from seven starts. Comes off a (25.60) win last time, scoring by 4 lengths in a Grade 5 over 455m at this track. Expected to be in the finish. BOMB LUCA (8) hit the frame last time at this track but just a few starts ago ran blistering time when scoring over 512m at Mt Gambier in 29.59. Rates a leading chance if runs up to recent winning time. NOLA KEEPING (2) stalked the lead from a low draw and fought on well to finish half a length back in second (25.95) at this track in a Grade 5 over 455m. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Can measure up. HUNTSMAN (7) has been going along well and was strongly fancied last time but could only manage third (25.99) at this track. Likely to be in the finish again.
